{"tid":1437701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Witness Hong Kong 機場展覽 10-11/8","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:05:55.000Z","uid":296449,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f94969747cc85d905379c43f88989fe40bd3eaea","tid":1437701,"uid":296449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"話說上次大家係度組隊搞展覽，展示我地呢幾個月以黎反送中運動。<br />\n而個展覽聽日終於開始啦！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3A0P9wi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3A0P9wi.jpg&h=4105cac7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsGLHRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsGLHRk.jpg&h=b215bebd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APc7bKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPc7bKF.jpg&h=b838f7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XNi2Rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XNi2Rn.jpg&h=522b1ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWzNbKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWzNbKH.jpg&h=970b57c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jV1LHRo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjV1LHRo.jpg&h=29e76436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活動名稱:  Witness HongKong Exhibition<br />\n日期:  8月10日, 11日<br />\n地點:  香港國際機場接機大堂<br />\n目的:   向世界宣示警暴的證據，突顯香港人的抗爭精神，引起國際輿論<br />\n對象:  旅客<br />\n<br />\n形式：  以機場手推車為載具，用數名full gear 人士向沿途人士展示及介紹近日的衝突及警方之暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n今次展覽假如成功，日後將會係18區巡迴展覽，請大家多多支持！！！"},{"pid":"255d108df6acdc867423f972e69781ca5e259bca","tid":1437701,"uid":296449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dee3db159f3e391fa2f59c3349b7bb52257125fd","tid":1437701,"uid":296449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a4094e29bbd0f8e2b973f26f